9398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9936205293020296, \"rank\": 0.006420313934579829, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a storm\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 191}, {\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 206}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic journey\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Championships\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"gender eligibility tests\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A matter for which, notably, no irrefutable evidence has been presented.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A matter\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"no irrefutable evidence\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At just 25, Khelif not only made history by securing Algeria's first female boxing gold with her resounding 5-0 victory over Yang Liu in the women's 66kg category but also became the centre of contention as the Games progressed.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9998656005438958, \"rank\": 0.00011278437733270486, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834675861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501