"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"the vitriol\", \"from\": 957, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"her direction\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"rampant speculation\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"her gender\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics experience\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After her triumph in Paris, the Algerian now has set her sights on a new challenge in the ring - turning pro.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974434104, \"rank\": 2.556519241002095e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9971983433575031, \"rank\": 0.002614512373525501, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her triumph\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"her sights\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1129}, {\"ngram\": \"a new challenge\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring - turning pro\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addressing the media on Sunday, she declared: \\\"I would like to hold a press conference today to share with you my success story with the media family and young women who watch me.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"a press conference\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1262}, {\"ngram\": \"my success story\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"the media family\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"young women\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a documentary being prepared about my success story and it will be shown on international platforms.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a documentary\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1380}, {\"ngram\": \"my success story\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"international platforms\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1466}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will soon enter the world of professional boxing, I have many offers.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"professional boxing\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"many offers\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently, I have not made up my mind about where I will enter professional boxing.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"professional boxing\", \"from\": 1603, \"to\": 1622}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But very soon I will take this step, we as Algerians would like to see our level in the field of professionalism.\\\"\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this step\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"Algerians\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"our level\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1717}, {\"ngram\": \"professionalism\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the month, there was a flurry of false reports that Khelif had been stripped of her Olympic glory, which triggered theWorld Boxing Organisation to clarify the situation firmly.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 0.9999999995739017, \"rank\": 4.25900559957202e-10, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"typ